*μέγας / megas / meg'-as
=== Etymology ===

*Including the prolonged forms, femine [[μεγάλη]] megalē, plural [[μέγάλοι]] megaloi, etc.; compare also [[μέγιστος]] {{GG|3176}}, [[μείζων]] {{GG|3187}} 

=== Adjective ===

*[[big]] (literally or figuratively, in a very wide application): 
*(+ fear) exceedingly, [[great]] (-est), [[high]], large, loud, [[mighty]], + (be) sore (afraid), strong, X to years.